Field Documentation

uint16_t _ZclSeTunnelSupportedProtocol_t::manufacturerCode

A code that is allocated by the ZigBee Alliance, relating the manufacturer to a device and - for tunneling - a manufacturer specific protocol. A value of 0xFFFF indicates a standard (i.e. non- manufacturer specific) protocol.

Definition at line 710 of file zclSmartEnergyTunnelCluster.h.

uint8_t _ZclSeTunnelSupportedProtocol_t::protocolId

An enumeration representing the identifier of the metering communication protocol for the supported tunnel. See ZSE Profile Spec. r17, Table D.67.
